<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>flask sample app | サーバエラー</title>
    <style>
        * {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        a {
        text-decoration: none;
        }

        li {
        list-style: none;
        }

        body {
        font-family: Avenir Next;
        }

        .header {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: space-between;
        background-color: #000000;
        color: #fff;
        height: 100px;
        }

        .header_logo {
        float: left;
        padding-left: 40px;
        }

        .header_logo img {
        float: left;
        max-width: 10%;
        max-height: 10%;
        display: block;
        padding: 10px 10px 10px 10px;
        }

        .header_list {
        font-size: 36px;
        display: flex;
        float: right;
        }

        .header_list a {
        color: #fff;
        }

        a.btn {
        text-decoration: none;
        color:rgb(255, 255, 255);
        }

        a.btn:hover {
        color: aquamarine;
        }

        .Home {
        padding-right: 50px;
        background-color: #000000;
        margin-right: 10px;
        }

        .main {
        padding: 20px 20px 20px 20px;
        background-color: #ffffff;
        height: auto;
        }

        .main h1 {
        font-size: 30px;
        padding: 20px 20px 20px 20px;
        }

        .section-title {
        border-bottom: 3px solid #dee7ec;
        }

        .main_contents {
        padding: 20px 20px 50px 20px;
        }

        .main_contents p {
        font-size: 22px;
        }

        .footer {
        background-color: #2f5167;
        color: #fff;
        height: 120px;
        padding: 40px 40px 40px 40px;
        }

        .footer p {
        font-size: 18px;
        }
        .error-wrapper {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 60px 20px;
        }
        .error-code {
            font-size: 44px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #e74c3c;
        }
        .error-message {
            font-size: 28px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        .error-btn {
            margin-top: 40px;
            padding: 12px 32px;
            font-size: 20px;
            border: 2px solid #2f5167;
            border-radius: 6px;
            background: #2f5167;
            color: #fff;
            cursor: pointer;
        }
        .error-btn:hover {
            background: #fff;
            color: #2f5167;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <div class="header_logo">
        </div>        
        <div class="header_list">
            <a href="/" class="btn Home">Home</a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="main">
        <div class="error-wrapper">
            <div class="error-code">500 Error</div>
            <div class="error-message">
                There was a problem on the server side.<br>
                Please try again in a few minutes.
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
        <p>Python + Flask + MySQL を使った CRUD アプリケーションです</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
